            <li>Secure, cloud-based architecture with 99.9% uptime</li>
            <li>Role-based access control with advanced permissions</li>
            <li>Intelligent appointment scheduling and resource allocation</li>
            <li>Comprehensive electronic health records (EHR) system</li>
            <li>Automated billing and insurance claim processing</li>
            <li>Real-time analytics and reporting dashboard</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Learn More About Our System</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Our Key Features</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i>
              </div>
              <h4>Doctor Management</h4>
              <p>Efficiently manage doctor schedules, specialties, and availability with our intuitive interface and
                automated notifications.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-procedures"></i>
              </div>
              <h4>Patient Care</h4>
              <p>Comprehensive patient records including medical history, prescriptions, lab results, and treatment
                plans in one secure location.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i>
              </div>
              <h4>Appointment System</h4>
              <p>Smart scheduling that prevents conflicts, sends reminders, and allows online booking for improved
