            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-pills"></i>
              </div>
              <h4>Pharmacy Integration</h4>
              <p>Seamless connection with pharmacy systems for electronic prescriptions and medication management.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
              </div>
              <h4>Analytics Dashboard</h4>
              <p>Real-time data visualization and reporting tools to monitor performance metrics and make informed
