              <div class="testimonial-role">Patient since 2018</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
              <p class="testimonial-text">"As a doctor, I appreciate how the system organizes patient records and
                streamlines prescriptions. It has significantly reduced paperwork and improved my clinic's efficiency."
              </p>
              <div class="testimonial-author">Dr. Priya Sharma</div>
              <div class="testimonial-role">Cardiologist</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
              <p class="testimonial-text">"The billing transparency is excellent. I can view all my medical expenses and
                insurance claims in one place, and the payment process is very convenient."</p>
